OL,3,CVillagers near Bristol and Bath fear
OL,4,Ctraffic chaos as essential work closes
OL,5,CM4
OL,7,FVillagers near Bristol and Bath have
OL,8,Fsaid they are fearing an onslaught of
OL,9,Ftraffic ahead of a planned closure of
OL,10,Fa major motorway.
OL,12,FThe M4 - between junction 18 for Bath
OL,13,Fand 19 for the M32 into Bristol - will
OL,14,Fbe shut in both directions from 7pm on
OL,15,FFriday 18 October until 6am on Monday
OL,16,F21 October, with diversion routes in
OL,17,Fplace.
