OL,4,Ctraffic chaos as essential work closes
OL,5,CM4
OL,7,FNational Highways said the work is
OL,8,Fessential to allow contractors to dig
OL,9,Fa trench under the motorway as part of
OL,10,Fthe work on the A432 Badminton Road
OL,11,FBridge.
OL,13,FIt will allow utilities, currently
OL,14,Fhoused within the bridge, to be
OL,15,Fdiverted before the structure is
OL,16,Fdemolished next year.
OL,18,FBut some residents have told ITV West
OL,19,FCountry they are worried the closure
OL,20,Fwill cause "carnage" in local villages.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
