OL,3,CVillagers near Bristol and Bath fear
OL,4,Ctraffic chaos as essential work closes
OL,5,CM4
OL,7,FAndy Banwell, a resident of the small
OL,8,Fvillage of Hinton, near Bath, said:
OL,9,F"We get 44-ton trucks coming down here
OL,10,Fnow and use the excuse of the satnav.
OL,11,FBut they get stuck and that closes the
OL,12,Fvillage off from one end.
OL,14,F"If you put the motorway traffic
OL,15,Fbehind it, that really is going to be
OL,16,Fbad. The motorway is busy 24 hours a
OL,17,Fday so we're going to see people using
OL,18,Ftheir satnavs, coming down here all
OL,19,Fweekend."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
