OL,5,CM4
OL,7,FThe official diversion takes drivers
OL,8,Fsouth of the M4 through Wick, Warmley,
OL,9,FEmersons Green and Bromley Heath.
OL,11,FNational Highways said the closure is
OL,12,Flikely to cause substantial disruption.
OL,14,F"We understand it's going to be
OL,15,Fdisruptive for some people," Sean
OL,16,FWalsh, National Highways route
OL,17,Fmanager, said.
