OL,3,CVillagers near Bristol and Bath fear
OL,4,Ctraffic chaos as essential work closes
OL,5,CM4
OL,7,F"If you can avoid driving down the M4
OL,8,For in the locality over the weekend
OL,9,Fplease do so. If you can't, please
OL,10,Fallow extra time and plan
OL,11,Fappropriately and most importantly
OL,12,Fplease follow the sign diversions."
OL,14,FBuilt in 1966, the Badminton Road
OL,15,Fbridge was closed to traffic after a
OL,16,Fstructural investigation in July 2023
OL,17,Ffound an accelerated deterioration and
OL,18,Fcracking on the underside of the
OL,19,Fstructure.
